snippet.textDisplay:
This song will always be remembered as a song which holded my hand in the days when i needed the most. It was the song which i used to listen before going to sleep . It made me recall all the good memories with her.. Though she left me but yaad ha mujhe teri haarrr ada. Ahhh. And this was the song which introduced kaavish in my life.
Being an Indian i wish jafar would have been born in India.
The amount of pain he can convey through his voice is impeccable. Hats off man❤
